test-method.name: CCP_GlobalValidationMsgForNoData
test-method.description: Verify that appropriate validation message appears when user clicks on 'Create Case' button without entering any data in mandatory fields, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_DefaultInfoMsgOnLOcationTile
test-method.description: Verify that an information message appears by deafult, when no location is selected, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_SearchAndAddAddress
test-method.description: Verify that user is able to add a location from 'Enter Address, APN or drop a Pin on the Map' combo box, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_OpenAddAddressManuallyPopup
test-method.description: Verify that 'Add Address Manually' popup opens up, after clicking on 'Add Address Manually' link, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_CloseAddAddressManuallyPopup
test-method.description: Verify that 'Add Address Manually' popup gets closed, when user clicks on 'Cross' icon or 'Cancel' button, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_AddTheAddressManually
test-method.description: Verify that the address gets added under 'Select Location' tile, after entering address details manually & clicking on 'Add Address' button, on 'Add Address Manually' popup.

test-method.name: CCP_EditAddedAddress
test-method.description: Verify that user is able to edit the location details, after clicking on the 'Edit' icon, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_UpdateAddressOnSaveButton
test-method.description: Verify that address gets updated, when user edits data and clicks on 'Save' button under 'Select Location' tile, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_AddressShouldntGetUpdatedOnCancelButton
test-method.description: Verify that address does not get updated, when user edits data and clicks on 'Cancel' button under 'Select Location' tile, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_OpenFlagAddressPopup
test-method.description: Verify that 'Flag Address' popup opens up for an unflagged address, when user clicks on 'Flagged?' toggle button, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_CloseFlagAddressPopup
test-method.description: Verify that 'Flag Address' popup gets closed, when user clicks on 'Cross' icon or 'Cancel' button, on 'Flag Address' popup.

test-method.name: CCP_VerifyFlagAddressButtonState
test-method.description: Verify that 'Flag address' button gets enabled, when user enters data in 'Reason to Flag the address' field, on 'Flag Address' popup.

test-method.name: CCP_VerifyFlaggedButtonState
test-method.description: Verify that 'Flagged?' toggle button gets enabled, when user clicks on 'Flag Address' button after entering data in the mandatory field, on 'Create Case' popup.

test-method.name: CCP_InfoMsgForNoViolation
test-method.description: Verify that an information message appears when no violation is added, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_ValidationMsgForNoViolation
test-method.description: Verify that appropriate validation message appears when user clicks on 'Create Case' button without adding any violation, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_InfoMsgForNonExistingData
test-method.description: Verify that an information message appears on entering non-existing data in 'Find a violation, article number or describe the issue' field, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_AddCustomIssueDescriptionField
test-method.description: Verify that 'Custom Issue Description' field gets added after entering data & clicking on 'Add custom issue description' link, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_validationMsgForEmptyCustomIssueDescriptionField
test-method.description: Verify that appropriate validation message appears when 'Custom Issue Description' field is blank, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_AddViolationWithoutEntity
test-method.description: Verify that Violation with no entity gets added under 'Add Violations' tile via search results of 'Find a violation, article number or describe the issue' combo box, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_AddViolationWithEntity

test-method.name: CCP_SearchAndAddViolation
test-method.description: Verify that user is able to add a violation after selecting an option from 'Find and add existing Entity' combo box, on Violation popup.

test-method.name: CCP_VerifyAddAnotherViolationLink
test-method.description: Verify that 'Add Another <Violation>' link appears under each added Violation type, under 'Add Violations' tile, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_DeleteAddedViolation
test-method.description: Verify that previously added violation gets deleted, when user clicks on the 'Delete' icon under 'Add Violations' tile, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_OpenEditViolationPopup
test-method.description: Verify that 'Edit <Violation>' popup opens up, when user clicks on 'Edit' icon under 'Add Violations' tile, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_UploadPhotoForViolation
test-method.description: Verify that a photo gets uploaded, when user selects a photo after clicking on 'Upload' button, on 'Edit <Violation>' popup.

test-method.name: CCP_VerifyReplaceButtonPresence
test-method.description: Verify that the 'Upload' button converts into 'Replace' button, when user uploads a photo, on 'Edit <Violation>' popup.

test-method.name: CCP_DeleteAddedPhoto
test-method.description: Verify that the added photo gets deleted, when user clicks on the 'Delete' icon, on 'Edit <Violation>' popup.

test-method.name: CCP_VerifyTotalViolationsCount
test-method.description: Verify that total count along with '<Violation with entity>' count of added violations appear beside 'Add Violations' tile's header, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_OpenViolationListingPopup
test-method.description: Verify that respective '<Violation> Listing' popup opens up, when user clicks on '<n> <Violation>' link next to 'Add Violation' tile header, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_CloseViolationListingPopup
test-method.description: Verify that '<Violation> Listing' popup gets closed, when user clicks on 'Cancel' button or 'Cross' icon, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_OpenCreateAContactPopup
test-method.description: Verify that 'Create a Contact' popup opens up, when user clicks on 'Add Contact' field > 'Create a new contact' link, on 'Create Case' popup.

test-method.name: CCP_ValidationMsgForNodataInNameField
test-method.description: Verify that appropriate validation message appears when 'Create Contact' button is clicked without entering data in the mandatory field, on 'Create a Contact' popup.

test-method.name: CCP_CloseCreateAContactPopup
test-method.description: Verify that 'Create a Contact' popup gets closed , when user clicks on 'Cancel' button, on 'Create Case' popup.

test-method.name: CCP_AddNewContact
test-method.description: Verify that user is able to add new Legal contact under 'Contacts' section on the CCP.

test-method.name: CCP_OpenEditContactPopup
test-method.description: Verify that 'Edit Contact' popup opens up for newly created contact, when user clicks on 'Edit' icon, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_DeleteAddedContact
test-method.description: Verify that previously added contact gets deleted, when user clicks on the 'Delete' icon, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_VerifyTotalContactCount
test-method.description: Verify that accurate count of added contacts appear beside 'Contacts' tile's header, on 'Create Case' popup.

test-method.name: CCP_VerifyViolationAttachmentsPresence
test-method.description: Verify that attachments added to the 'Add Violations' tile also appear on the 'Attachments' tile, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_OpenAddAttachmentsPopup
test-method.description: Verify that 'Add Attachments' popup opens up, when user clicks on the 'Image' icon under 'Attachments' tile, on 'Create Case' page.

test-method.name: CCP_VerifyAttachmentsPreview
test-method.description: Verify that attachment's preview appears, when user selects an attachment after clicking on 'Browse file' link or 'Camera' button, on 'Add Attachments' popup.

test-method.name: CCP_OpenCloseAddAttachmentsPopup
test-method.description: Verify that 'Close Add Attachments' confirmation popup opens up, when user clicks on 'Cross' icon or 'Cancel' button after selecting an attachment, on 'Add Attachments' popup.

test-method.name: CCP_CloseAddAttachmentsPopup
test-method.description: Verify that 'Add Attachments' popup gets closed, when user clicks on 'Yes, Close' button, on 'Close Add Attachment' confirmation popup.

test-method.name: CCP_ReopenAddAttachmentsPopup
test-method.description: Verify that 'Add Attachments' popup reopens, when user clicks on 'No, Don't Close' button, on 'Close Add Attachment' confirmation popup.

test-method.name: SubmissionSettings_VerifyToggleButtonsState
test-method.description: Verify that user is able to select any 'Closing the code case automatically closes the submission?' toggle buttons, on 'Submission Settings' page.

test-method.name: SubmissionSettings_VerifyDiscardButtonFunctionality
test-method.description: Verify that the changes do not get saved, when user clicks on 'Discard Changes' button, on 'Submission Settings' page.

test-method.name: SubmissionSettings_VerifyChangesGetSaved
test-method.description: Verify that the changes get saved, when user clicks on 'Save Changes' button, on 'Submission Settings' page.

test-method.name: SubmissionSettings_VerifyAutomaticClosingOfLinkedSubmission
test-method.description: Verify that Submission gets closed automatically on closing the linked Case, when 'Closing the code case automatically closes the submission?' toggle button is set to 'Yes', on 'Submission Settings' page.

test-method.name: SubmissionSettings_VerifyCaseDoesntCloseForNoToggle
test-method.description: Verify that Submission does not get closed automatically on closing the linked Case, when 'Closing the code case automatically closes the submission?' toggle button is set to 'No', on 'Submission Settings' page.
